Join food editor Hilary Biller and rate ready-made "kiddies" meals sold in supermarkets. It's fun and FREE. Please note the invitation is open to children between the ages of 6 and 10 and is limited to ONE parent/ guardian accompanied by ONE child. All adult tasters will go home with a copy of the latest Sunday Times Cookbook as a thank-you.WHEN: Saturday April 8, from 10am to 1pm.INTERESTED? E-mail your contact details and the name and age of your child to Philantu Nkanunu, NkanunuP@timesmedia.co.za, by April 5 and we will confirm your attendance.